---
// Footer.astro
const links = ['Tratamientos', 'Horarios de atención', 'Instagram', 'Políticas de privacidad'];
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer style="background:#F0E0C7; border-top: 1px solid #9B7A73;">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-14">

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-10">

      <!-- Col 1: Brand -->
      <div>
        <span class="block text-2xl tracking-widest mb-4" style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; color:#6B2F1E; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.15em;">
          GO<span style="color:#AF7127;">ESSENCE</span>
        </span>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-xs" style="color:#934829; font-weight:300;">
          Estética y Spa. Elevando el estándar de la medicina estética a través de la innovación científica y el cuidado consciente.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Col 2: Quick links -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-6" style="color:#AF7127;">Enlaces Rápidos</p>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          {links.map(l => (
            <li>
              <a href="#" class="text-sm transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-opacity-60" style="color:#6B2F1E; font-weight:300;">{l}</a>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Col 3: Contact -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-6" style="color:#AF7127;">Contacto</p>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" class="shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <circle cx="8" cy="6" r="3" stroke="#AF7127" stroke-width="1.2"/>
              <path d="M3 13C3 10.2 5.2 8 8 8C10.8 8 13 10.2 13 13" stroke="#AF7127" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm" style="color:#6B2F1E; font-weight:300;">Barranquilla, Colombia</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" class="shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <path d="M2 3C2 3 4.5 2 8 2C11.5 2 14 3 14 3V12C14 12 11.5 11 8 11C4.5 11 2 12 2 12V3Z" stroke="#AF7127" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm" style="color:#6B2F1E; font-weight:300;">+57 314 713 8877</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" class="shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <rect x="2" y="2" width="12" height="12" stroke="#AF7127" stroke-width="1.2"/>
              <circle cx="8" cy="8" r="3" stroke="#AF7127" stroke-width="1.2"/>
              <circle cx="12.5" cy="3.5" r="0.8" fill="#AF7127"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm" style="color:#6B2F1E; font-weight:300;">@GOESSENCE</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Copyright -->
    <div style="border-top: 1px solid #9B7A73;" class="pt-8 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-start lg:items-center justify-between gap-3">
      <p class="text-xs" style="color:#934829; font-weight:300;">
        &copy; {year} Todos los derechos reservados GO Essence Estética y Spa.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs" style="color:#AF7127; opacity:0.7;">
        Diseñado con intención.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</footer>
